---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Authentication Mechanisms
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Username and Password -> Form, Basic, Digest
-

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Username and Password
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Form Authentication
- username and password being provided through an html form

# HTTP Basic
- Authorization Header

# Digest
- Deprecated!
- Passwords must be stored in plaintext, encrypted, or an MD5 format. All of these
  storage formats are considered insecure.




